	<h1>Amakozi Reporting product released!</h1>
	<h3>Friday, 30 September 2011</h3>
	<p>Amakozi Technologies is proud to announce the release of it <a href="/products/reporting.aspx" alt="Click here to read more about the product">Reporting</a> product.</p>

<h4>The SDL Tridion Release</h4>
<p>The Amakozi Reporting product is designed and built to be "skinned" under any company brand, allowing Amakozi to sell the product under OEM agreements.  The first branded version was released today as well, which is the SDL Tridion Reporting brand.  The SDL Tridion release consists out of:</p>
<ul>
<li>a Content Archive feature to collect SDL Tridion reporting data.</li>
<li>an extension library integrating fully with the SDL Tridion Content Manager Explorer</li>
<li>a wide range of data sources to build various kinds of reports (UGC, Audience Manager, Archived Content, Broker Content, etc)</li>
</ul>

<h4>Tailored for all sources</h4>
<p>The unique architecture of the Amakozi Reporting product allow customers to consume any data source to report on.  Version 1.0, known as the "demo version", already support the development of custom data sources.  Out of the box we will deliver data sources consuming data from Omniture, Google Analytics, Direct Database queries, and a wide range of SDL Tridion libraries.  In the future Amakozi (and users of the product) will develop more data libraries.  These libraries will be downloadable from www.amakozi.com. </p>

<br/>

<p>Amakozi is thankfull for the hard work by our R&D team, making this product a great success.</p>

